BH/Blastrage


BH and Blastrage arrive at the maximal base, in the skimmer the 
brought. They pull out their biggest guns.

BH aims at the ark with his 2 rocket launchers. He fires 2 rockets.
He 
then looks at Blastrage. "Use the Skiimers computer to tell where the 
weak pionts are in the maximals ship."

Blastrage hears BH's command. "Right away." Blastrage punches a few 
keys and then looks up to BH. "Right there." He says as 5 gernades 
lands on the side of the ark.
